description:
Billy Mays was the first spokesperson for OxiClean™. Watch as he shows the world the power of OxiClean™ Versatile Stain Remover, which uses the power of oxygen to remove difficult stains.

Learn more about OxiClean™: https://www.oxiclean.com/
Learn more about OxiClean™ Versatile Stain Remover: https://www.oxiclean.com/en/products/stain-fighters/oxiclean-versatile-stain-remover

Note: This video is for archival purposes only. Please refer to our newer videos for current product information and usage.
